Catch the phishing website based on URL.
31 features are extracted from the URL based on the research by Rami M. Mohammad, Fadi Thabtah and Lee McCluskey. The clear description see "Phishing Websites Feaures.docx".
Several classification models are tested: Navie Bayes, Logsitic regression, SVM,LinearSVC, KNN, Random Forest.
Evaluated by confusion matrix and cost-benefit analysis. Random Forest is selected at last with Recall of 0.98 and precision of 0.97.
"phishing detection introduction.pdf" is the presentation material of this project. It tells the overall story.
A Sankey diagram is created in Tableau Public as the implementation guide.
https://public.tableau.com/profile/sakura7863#!/vizhome/3333_0/mysheet
